Odette Barencey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odette_Barencey 0 Odette Barencey (20 August 1893 – 4 March 1981) was a French film actress. She appeared in 53 films between 1927 and 1958. She was married to the actor Marcel Barencey. Odette_Barencey ( 20_August_1893 – 4_March_1981 ) was a_French_film_actress . She appeared in 53_films between 1927_and_1958 .
